summary: I know this isn’t how it works, but I feel like I’m not smart enough/a good enough writer to do Good Omens fic.  Because if I...
body:
I know this isn’t how it works, but I feel like I’m not smart enough/a good enough writer to do Good Omens fic.  Because if I did, I’d want to do it in the style of the book, and that’s not in my skill set so…shrug emoji.

But a fic I really want to read/write is one in which Crowley and Aziraphale are slightly less incompetent and become godfathers to the actual Antichrist and help raise Adam over the years.  If anyone knows a fic like that, could you hook a girl up~?
